milestones.description: Aizaz Khan and Haseeb Amjad's 50-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 47 between Manoj Cheruparambil and Afzaal Haider
Tanwir Afzal and Aizaz Khan's 24-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Afzaal Haider and Najeeb Amar
Atkinson has become the top scorer for HKG in ODIs with 148 runs, going past Tabarak Dar's 101
Haseeb Amjad has broken the record for most sixes (4) in ODIs for HKG, going past Babar Hayat's 3
Atkinson has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for HKG, going past Tim Smart's 2
Atkinson's 59 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for HKG), surpassing Babar Hayat's 53
Atkinson has broken the record for most ODIs (3) as captain for HKG, going past Rahul Sharma
